Class Attribute

java.lang.Object
com.fns.grivet.model.Attribute
All Implemented Interfaces:
Auditable<String>, Serializable
@Entity public class Attribute extends Object implements Auditable<String>
An Attribute participates in the definition of a property in a ClassAttribute. One or more ClassAttribute may share an Attribute.

Chris Phillipson
